cu.explanation_en: Num_Threads_PDSCH changed from 8 to 0, which is below the valid range, causing PDSCH processing thread allocation failures and downlink data handling issues.
cu.explanation_zh: Num_Threads_PDSCH 从 8 更改为 0，低于有效范围，导致 PDSCH 处理线程分配失败和下行数据处理问题。

du.explanation_en: remote_n_portc changed from 501 to 0, which is below the valid port range, causing F1 control plane interface binding failures and preventing DU-CU communication.
du.explanation_zh: remote_n_portc 从 501 更改为 0，低于有效端口范围，导致 F1 控制平面接口绑定失败，阻止 DU-CU 通信。
